WITH A GASTROINTESTINAL ROBOT
SURGEON WHILE I WAS ALWAYS GONE.

12:43.230 --> 12:44.965
SHE'S SLEEPING
WITH SOMEONE ELSE.

12:44.998 --> 12:46.800
NOT THAT COMPLICATED.

12:46.834 --> 12:48.135
WHY'D YOU RUN?

12:55.843 --> 12:58.912
THERE WAS THIS GUY
I USED TO KNOW ‐‐

12:58.946 --> 13:00.681
UH, GUILLERMO.

13:00.714 --> 13:02.516
GARCIA GOMEZ?
YEAH.

13:02.549 --> 13:04.318
HE AND I ‐‐

13:04.351 --> 13:06.687
YOU SLEPT
WITH GUILLERMO.

13:06.720 --> 13:10.824
THAT NIGHT, PILAR ESCORTED ME
OUT OF THE PARTY.

13:10.858 --> 13:12.793
GUILLERMO WAS THERE,
AND SHE ‐‐

13:12.826 --> 13:14.194
THIS IS MEXICALI.

13:14.228 --> 13:17.097
THOSE ARE MEMBERS
OF THE ARELLANO‐FELIX FAMILY.

13:17.130 --> 13:19.266
THIS IS THE NIGHT
OF THE PARTY.

13:20.968 --> 13:23.136
GUILLERMO WAS IN MEXICO.

13:25.606 --> 13:28.275
STOP IT!
STOP IT!

13:28.308 --> 13:30.244
IT'S ALL BACKED UP
OFF‐SITE.

13:30.277 --> 13:32.346
DEAL'S OFF!

13:32.980 --> 13:35.449
WHO DOES THIS?!

13:35.482 --> 13:37.451
I'M GLAD I DIDN'T GO
TO HIGH SCHOOL WITH YOU.

13:37.484 --> 13:39.586
SPOILED CUNT LIKE YOU.

13:39.620 --> 13:42.089
WOULDN'T EVEN GET
A CUP OF COFFEE WITH ME!

13:42.122 --> 13:43.390
YOU KNOW WHAT?

13:43.423 --> 13:45.492
I DON'T HAVE TO DEAL
WITH BITCHES LIKE YOU ANYMORE.

13:45.526 --> 13:47.394
I'M AN ADULT NOW.

13:50.464 --> 13:52.633
I DON'T NEED YOU ANYMORE.
I'LL WRITE WHATEVER I WANT.

13:52.666 --> 13:55.936
LEAVE.
NO, NO. THE DEAL'S BACK ON.
I NEED THE MONEY.

13:55.969 --> 13:58.739
DEAL'S OFF. GO.

13:58.772 --> 13:59.806
GET OUT.

13:59.840 --> 14:01.408
[ DOOR SLAMS ]

14:01.441 --> 14:03.477
FUCKING BITCH. GOD.

14:03.510 --> 14:06.980
YOU GOT TO TAKE ME WITH YOU.
I GOT MONEY.

14:07.014 --> 14:08.649
WE'RE GETTING MONEY.
HOOMAN HERE OWES MY MOM.

14:08.682 --> 14:11.785
SORRY, BRO. I CAN'T SELL
ANY LEG SPREADER WHILE
I'M HIDING OUT HERE.

14:11.818 --> 14:13.954
HOW MUCH DO YOU HAVE?

14:13.987 --> 14:16.423
LET ME SHOW YOU.

14:17.925 --> 14:20.227
KIDS TIP OVER MY CARTS.

14:20.260 --> 14:23.096
AND ONCE ‐‐ ONCE ‐‐
I GET A CHRISTMAS GIFT

14:23.130 --> 14:24.431
FROM ONE OF MY CUSTOMERS.

14:24.464 --> 14:25.966
AND YOU KNOW
WHAT IT WAS?
POOP?

14:25.999 --> 14:29.136
POOP. POOP. POOP!

14:29.169 --> 14:33.340
SO, SOMETIMES I JUST
BRING THE MAIL HOME.

14:35.909 --> 14:38.712
YOU HAVE TO BE
THE WORST MAILMAN EVER.

14:38.745 --> 14:41.281
YEP.

14:41.315 --> 14:44.952
I'M REALLY NOT ‐‐
NOT VERY GOOD.

14:44.985 --> 14:47.654
I HAVE PASSPORTS.

14:47.688 --> 14:49.756
SHOW ME.

14:55.863 --> 14:56.997
THAT IS NOT HIS.

14:57.030 --> 14:59.299
HUH? NO.
OF COURSE IT'S HIS.

14:59.333 --> 15:01.602
THAT DICK
IS A MAGIC MARKER.

15:01.635 --> 15:03.370
HOOMAN HAS A CRAYON.

15:03.403 --> 15:06.039
I TOOK HIM TO THE BATHS.
[ SCOFFS ]

15:06.073 --> 15:09.042
THE RUDE ASSHOLE NEVER EVEN
TOOK OFF HIS BLUETOOTH.

15:09.076 --> 15:11.144
NO, NO, YOU'RE NOT
ACCOUNTING FOR EDEMA.

15:11.178 --> 15:14.147
IT'S FLOATING IN LIQUID,
SO IT EXPANDED ‐‐ EDEMA.

15:14.181 --> 15:18.051
I ASKED YOU TO KILL
ONE WORTHLESS IDIOT,

15:18.085 --> 15:19.920
AND YOU TRY
TO DECEIVE ME?

15:19.953 --> 15:21.989
GO, BEFORE I CUT OFF
YOUR PENIS!

15:22.022 --> 15:23.557
OHH! WE HAD A DEAL!

15:23.590 --> 15:26.727
JAKA‐COCK FOR PASSPORTS.
I HELD UP MY END.

15:26.760 --> 15:28.128
DAOUD MAHMUD,
WHAT DID YOU DO?

15:28.161 --> 15:30.464
I WAS JUST LOOKING OUT
FOR YOUR BEST INTERESTS.

15:30.497 --> 15:33.200
HE WASN'T GOOD ENOUGH
FOR YOU. HONEY!

15:34.902 --> 15:39.072
UGH!
YOU ARE DEAD TO ME!

15:40.574 --> 15:42.576
ADARA! PRINCESS!

15:45.946 --> 15:48.882
MY HUSBAND WOULD HIRE
A DISCOUNT HITMAN.

15:48.916 --> 15:51.385
EVEN THE JEWS THINK
THAT MAN IS CHEAP.

15:51.418 --> 15:54.421
[ CHUCKLES ] THAT'S A GOOD LINE.
OFFENSIVE BUT ‐‐

15:54.454 --> 15:55.656
SHUT UP.

15:55.689 --> 15:59.359
YOU DECEIVED HIM, BUT I WILL
GIVE YOU THE PASSPORTS.

15:59.393 --> 16:01.228
OH, WOW. THANKS.
THANK YOU.

16:01.261 --> 16:05.098
AND I WILL ONLY
CHARGE YOU $5,000.

16:05.132 --> 16:08.969
I'VE BEEN ON THE WAITING LIST
FOR A BIRKIN BAG FOREVER,

16:09.002 --> 16:11.004
AND MY NAME JUST CAME UP.

16:16.977 --> 16:19.780
HOW DID YOU END UP
IN DEARBORN?

16:19.813 --> 16:21.915
I THOUGHT ARABS
HATED COLD WEATHER.

16:21.949 --> 16:24.952
WHY DO YOU DESERVE TO BE HERE
MORE THAN I DO?

16:24.985 --> 16:26.353
SIMPLE MATH.

16:26.386 --> 16:28.822
YOU PEOPLE DIDN'T GET HERE
TILL THE '70s.

16:28.856 --> 16:30.624
MY PEOPLE HAVE BEEN HERE
FOREVER.

16:30.657 --> 16:31.625
OH, REALLY?

16:31.658 --> 16:34.228
WHAT ARE YOU, OTTAWA,
ANISHINABE, OR POTAWATOMI?

16:34.261 --> 16:36.730
OH, DON'T GIVE ME
THAT INDIAN CRAP.

16:36.763 --> 16:39.800
HAVE YOU BEEN TO THE
SOARING EAGLE CASINO LATELY?

16:39.833 --> 16:43.203
I WENT LAST MONTH
TO SEE JEFF DUNHAM.

16:43.237 --> 16:46.273
THE TICKETS ALONE
COST 55 BUCKS.

16:46.306 --> 16:50.844
ADD TO THAT THE ROOM,
A LITTLE BUFFET, A LITTLE CRAPS.

16:50.878 --> 16:53.280
THE REAL TRAIL OF TEARS
IS ME

16:53.313 --> 16:55.482
GOING BACK AND FORTH
TO THE ATM ALL NIGHT.

16:55.516 --> 16:57.217
YOU WANT TO JOIN?

16:57.251 --> 17:00.254
WE'RE STEALING CHRISTMAS‐CARD
MONEY FROM THE PAST.

17:00.287 --> 17:02.823
NO, THANKS.
WHERE'S MOM?

17:02.856 --> 17:04.224
SHE'S NOT HERE.

17:04.258 --> 17:05.192
HERE.

17:05.225 --> 17:06.660
I SAID I DON'T WANT TO
OPEN ANYTHING.

17:06.693 --> 17:09.530
NO, IT'S YOUR PATERNITY RESULTS.
PICKED THEM UP TODAY.

17:14.468 --> 17:17.037
YO,
THIS ONE'S ADDRESSED TO ME!

17:18.872 --> 17:22.042
I GOT INTO COLLEGE?!

17:24.778 --> 17:26.246
[ KNOCK ON WINDOW ]

17:26.280 --> 17:28.815
Nancy:
CAN I COME BACK IN?

17:28.849 --> 17:31.785
FUCK OFF!

17:31.818 --> 17:37.224
[ SIGHS ]

17:37.257 --> 17:39.726
SORRY ABOUT YOUR CAMERA.

17:39.760 --> 17:41.929
FILMED MY SON'S BIRTH
WITH IT.

17:41.962 --> 17:43.564
YOU WAIT TO PUBLISH.

17:43.597 --> 17:44.698
I KNOW.

17:44.731 --> 17:45.966
YOU DON'T SAY
WHERE WE'RE GOING.

17:45.999 --> 17:47.401
I DON'T KNOW
WHERE YOU'RE GOING.

17:47.434 --> 17:50.871
GOOD.
WHAT'S MY NAME GONNA BE?

17:50.904 --> 17:52.840
WHAT DO YOU WANT
YOUR NAME TO BE?

17:52.873 --> 17:56.410
CELIA HODES.

17:56.443 --> 17:58.912
[ CHUCKLES ]

17:58.946 --> 18:01.448
WHAT?
WHAT IS IT?

18:03.450 --> 18:05.485
[ BEEP ]

18:05.519 --> 18:07.454
THEY'LL FIND YOU.

18:07.487 --> 18:08.589
I DON'T THINK SO.

18:08.622 --> 18:11.758
PILAR JUST DOESN'T DISAPPEAR
AND NO ONE HAS TO ANSWER.

18:11.792 --> 18:13.427
SHE'S A LEGITIMATE
BUSINESSWOMAN.

18:13.460 --> 18:15.896
SOMEONE HAS TO ANSWER.

18:15.929 --> 18:18.265
YEAH, WELL,
THEN WE'LL KEEP RUNNING.

18:18.298 --> 18:19.967
IT'S AN OPEN
MURDER INVESTIGATION,

18:20.000 --> 18:22.469
AND NOT JUST THE COPS ‐‐
FBI.

18:22.503 --> 18:24.805
THEM.

18:24.838 --> 18:27.608
AND IF I'M COMING
TO THAT CONCLUSION ‐‐

18:27.641 --> 18:31.044
SHANE ‐‐
THEN OTHERS WILL, TOO.

18:31.078 --> 18:33.547
[ CHUCKLES SOFTLY ]

18:36.416 --> 18:39.052
[ SIGHS ]

18:39.086 --> 18:41.822
CAN I HAVE MY MONEY?

18:41.855 --> 18:46.126
PAYING FOR INTERVIEWS...
OUT OF POCKET.

18:46.159 --> 18:48.929
MY ENTIRE ADVANCE, GONE.

18:48.962 --> 18:51.198
GOD, THIS IS DEPRESSING.

18:52.733 --> 18:55.736
FRAN TARKENTON ‐‐
WHERE'D YOU PULL THAT FROM?

18:55.769 --> 18:58.172
OH. [ CHUCKLES ]

18:58.205 --> 18:59.873
YEAH, JUDAH LOVED HIM.

18:59.907 --> 19:01.875
HE HAD HIS, UH ‐‐
HIS SIGNED ROOKIE CARD

19:01.909 --> 19:03.310
BETWEEN TWO PIECES
OF GLASS.

19:03.343 --> 19:07.681
SAID WE WERE GONNA BUY
OUR RETIREMENT HOUSE
IN HAWAII WITH IT.

19:07.714 --> 19:09.583
I CHECKED ONLINE
NOT SO LONG AGO.

19:09.616 --> 19:13.086
IT'S WORTH LIKE...
$700.

19:13.120 --> 19:15.556
RIDICULOUS.
I MEAN, CAN YOU IMAGINE?

19:15.589 --> 19:17.591
I‐I HATE THE SUN.

19:17.624 --> 19:20.661
JUDAH WAS...SO...

19:22.963 --> 19:26.567
ANYWAY, I REALLY AM SORRY
ABOUT YOUR CAMERA.

19:26.600 --> 19:28.135
THAT WAS MEAN.

19:31.104 --> 19:33.440
GUESS YOUR WORD CLOUD
WAS RIGHT.

19:42.282 --> 19:43.650
WHY DIDN'T I KNOW
JOSH WAS GAY?

19:43.684 --> 19:46.687
I MEAN, EVEN AS A BABY,
HE LOOKED GAY. GAY BABY.

19:46.720 --> 19:48.522
OH, GOD.
I'M GOING BACK TO BED.

19:48.555 --> 19:50.858
YELL AT ME, DANA. GET MAD.
BUT DON'T KEEP IT IN.

19:50.891 --> 19:52.826
YOU'RE GONNA GIVE YOURSELF
BUTT CANCER.

19:52.860 --> 19:55.963
I'M NOT MAD AT YOU.

19:55.996 --> 19:57.764
I'M HAPPY.

19:57.798 --> 20:00.267
YOU MARRIED UNCLE PHIL FROM
"THE FRESH PRINCE OF BEL‐AIR."

20:00.300 --> 20:02.102
THAT'S AN OBVIOUS
CRY FOR HELP.

20:02.135 --> 20:05.405
WHY ARE YOU HERE, DOUG ‐‐
REALLY?

20:08.208 --> 20:09.943
TO GET MY PASSPORT.

20:09.977 --> 20:12.813
IT'S IN THE SAFETY DEPOSIT BOX
AT THE BANK.

20:12.846 --> 20:15.315
WE NEEDED BOTH KEYS
TO OPEN IT.

20:15.349 --> 20:16.517
HEY.

20:16.550 --> 20:18.852
OKAY. THERE IT IS.

20:18.886 --> 20:21.021
TAKE IT.
NOW YOU CAN LEAVE.

20:21.054 --> 20:23.123
JUST MAIL THEM BOTH BACK
WHEN YOU'RE DONE.

20:23.156 --> 20:25.859
I DON'T WANT THE PASSPORT
ANYMORE.

20:25.893 --> 20:27.928
I KNOW WHY GOD
KEPT ME ALIVE NOW.

20:27.961 --> 20:30.831
SEEING YOU AND JULIE ‐‐
JESSIE.

20:30.864 --> 20:32.299
I'M GONNA STAY HERE
WHERE I BELONG,

20:32.332 --> 20:34.501
AT THE HEAD OF THIS FAMILY,
RIGHT HERE IN AGRESTIC.

20:34.535 --> 20:37.471
IT'S CALLED RE‐GRESTIC NOW.

20:37.504 --> 20:39.273
THAT'S RE‐TARDED.

20:39.306 --> 20:44.478
YOU ARE NOT A PART
OF THIS FAMILY ANYMORE.

20:44.511 --> 20:48.815
YOU ARE JUST THE IDIOT MAN‐BABY
WHO WALKED OUT ON US.

20:48.849 --> 20:51.385
NOW, YOU RUINED MY LIFE
ONCE BEFORE,

20:51.418 --> 20:54.688
AND YOU ARE NOT
GONNA RUIN IT AGAIN!

20:56.456 --> 20:58.592
ARE YOU AS TURNED ON
AS I AM RIGHT NOW?

21:00.327 --> 21:01.628
UGH!

21:01.662 --> 21:02.930
OW!

21:02.963 --> 21:03.931
[ GROANING ]

21:03.964 --> 21:05.365
DAMN IT!

21:08.202 --> 21:10.437
DUDE, WHAT HAPPENED?

21:10.470 --> 21:14.107
I TOTALLY UNDERSTAND
THE EGO ISSUES INVOLVED

21:14.141 --> 21:16.677
WHEN IT COMES
TO ONE'S LOUISVILLE SLUGGER,

21:16.710 --> 21:18.879
BUT MAYBE
YOU COULD HAVE BEEN

21:18.912 --> 21:21.782
A LITTLE MORE IN THE BALLPARK,
SIZE‐WISE?

21:21.815 --> 21:24.751
MAN, WHAT'S THAT
SUNNI PERV DOING

21:24.785 --> 21:26.620
CHECKING OUT MY JUNK
ANYWAY?

21:26.653 --> 21:28.088
FUCK THAT WHOLE FAMILY!

21:28.121 --> 21:29.990
NO. GO TO HER.

21:30.023 --> 21:33.493
DON'T END UP DEAD AND ALONE
LIKE I'M GOING TO.

21:33.527 --> 21:37.197
MAYBE IF I SHOW HIM
I GOT INTO COLLEGE...

21:37.231 --> 21:39.299
AH.

21:39.333 --> 21:42.436
ALL RIGHT.
YOU GUYS HAVE BEEN DOPE.

21:42.469 --> 21:44.738
WISH ME LUCK.

21:46.406 --> 21:48.141
WHAT'S WITH YOU?

21:48.175 --> 21:50.043
I SAW A LOT
OF DEAD PEOPLE TODAY.

21:50.077 --> 21:51.979
KIND OF BATTLING
MY OWN MORTALITY.

21:52.012 --> 21:53.580
WHAT'S ARE YOU GUYS DOING?

21:53.614 --> 21:55.449
GETTING COPENHAGEN MONEY.

21:55.482 --> 21:57.117
SORT OF THOUGHT
WE'D FIND MORE.

21:57.150 --> 22:00.921
THAT? YEAH, THAT'S NOT GONNA
GET US PLANE TICKETS,
LET ALONE PASSPORTS.

22:00.954 --> 22:02.890
FUCK!
I GUESS COPENHAGEN'S OFF.

22:02.923 --> 22:04.525
NO. NO, IT'S NOT.

22:04.558 --> 22:08.428
PASSPORTS, PLANE TICKETS,
WHATEVER ELSE WE NEED ‐‐

22:08.462 --> 22:09.963
JUST GO GET IT.

22:09.997 --> 22:13.267
WAKE ME
WHEN IT'S TIME TO GO.

22:14.468 --> 22:17.571
UH, THIS WILL ONLY
COVER THE PASSPORTS.

22:17.604 --> 22:21.441
I'LL GET THE MONEY.
I'LL GET THE MONEY.

22:30.717 --> 22:32.219
[ SIGHS ]

22:34.755 --> 22:36.990
[ SNIFFLES,
EXHALES SHARPLY ]

22:37.024 --> 22:39.459
NANCE, I'LL BE HONEST ‐‐
TOO MUCH DEATH TODAY.

22:39.493 --> 22:40.260
[ CHUCKLES ]

22:40.294 --> 22:42.663
I'M SUDDENLY TERRIFIED
OF DYING

22:42.696 --> 22:44.631
AND LEAVING
YOU GUYS ALONE.

22:44.665 --> 22:47.901
I GOT THE TICKETS.

22:47.935 --> 22:49.736
AND DON'T ASK ME HOW.

22:49.770 --> 22:51.905
BUT SEVEN HOURS FROM NOW,

22:51.939 --> 22:55.142
WE'RE ALL FLYING TO COPENHAGEN
VIA PARIS.

22:55.175 --> 23:00.414
AND I HAVE ARRANGED IT SO THAT
YOU AND I GET TO SIT TOGETHER.

23:00.447 --> 23:02.616
I NEED TO TELL YOU
MY OFFICIAL END‐OF‐LIFE PLAN

23:02.649 --> 23:05.652
BEFORE SOMEONE'S STICKING
MY DICK IN A SOUP CONTAINER.

23:05.686 --> 23:08.755
SO, READY?

23:08.789 --> 23:11.058
OPEN BAR.

23:11.091 --> 23:12.626
BIG PHOTO OF ME.

23:12.659 --> 23:15.929
BOY, THOSE LAST‐MINUTE
TICKETS TO EUROPE COST A LOT.

23:15.963 --> 23:17.831
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

23:17.865 --> 23:20.167
OKAY, SO,
HERE'S THE TICKETS.

23:20.200 --> 23:22.035
I WANT MY ASHES
DIVIDED IN TWO ‐‐

23:22.069 --> 23:25.539
ONE HALF SET ADRIFT
ON AN ICE FLOE IN GLACIER BAY,

23:25.572 --> 23:29.009
THE OTHER HALF BLOWN
INTO NORM ENGERFELT'S FACE

23:29.042 --> 23:33.447
WITH THE WORDS
"ANUS BOTWIN SAYS HI."

23:33.480 --> 23:35.315
GRATITUDE EXPRESSED
THROUGH FELLATIO

23:35.349 --> 23:38.552
HAS NEVER BEEN REJECTED,
EVER, IN HISTORY.

23:38.585 --> 23:41.255
IF YOU DON'T FOLLOW ALL THIS
TO THE LETTER, I WILL HAUNT YOU.

23:41.288 --> 23:44.858
MURDER HALLUCINATIONS,
FLYING BABIES,

23:44.892 --> 23:46.793
GIANT HELLMOUTH
IN YOUR CLOSET ‐‐

23:46.827 --> 23:48.395
YEAH,
REAL NIGHTMARE SHIT.

23:48.428 --> 23:50.631
I'M GONNA GO PACK.

23:57.304 --> 24:01.041
CAN I LIE NEXT TO YOU
FOR A SECOND?

24:03.010 --> 24:07.581
I USED TO LOVE SLEEPING
BETWEEN YOU AND DAD.

24:09.016 --> 24:11.218
FELT SO SAFE.

24:13.253 --> 24:16.123
DOESN'T REALLY FEEL
LIKE ANYTHING NOW.

24:18.592 --> 24:22.162
AT LEAST I DON'T HAVE TO WORRY
ABOUT DROPPING DEAD AT 40

24:22.196 --> 24:23.830
FROM A BAD TICKER.

24:23.864 --> 24:26.433
LARS IS IN GREAT SHAPE.

24:33.607 --> 24:35.275
BYE, MOM.

24:36.910 --> 24:41.281
I SINCERELY WISH YOU
ALL GOOD THINGS.

25:02.302 --> 25:04.171
[ CRYING ]

25:10.944 --> 25:14.014
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

25:21.522 --> 25:25.058
ANDY! ANDY?

25:26.860 --> 25:29.096
HEY.
HOW WAS YOUR NAP?

25:29.129 --> 25:31.565
I'LL MEET YOU
AT THE AIRPORT.

25:31.598 --> 25:32.833
YOU KNOW WHAT TO DO.

25:32.866 --> 25:35.836
PLAN "A," PLAN "B,"
OR PLAN "C"?

25:35.869 --> 25:38.105
I'LL LET YOU KNOW.

25:38.138 --> 25:43.443
♪♪ TRUE LOVE WILL FIND YOU
IN THE END ♪♪

25:47.114 --> 25:52.019
♪♪ YOU'LL FIND OUT
JUST WHO WAS YOUR FRIEND ♪♪

25:54.354 --> 26:00.661
♪♪ DON'T BE SAD,
I KNOW YOU WILL ♪♪

26:00.694 --> 26:05.199
♪♪ BUT DON'T GIVE UP UNTIL ♪♪

26:05.232 --> 26:10.537
♪♪ TRUE LOVE WILL FIND YOU
IN THE END ♪♪

26:12.940 --> 26:19.513
♪♪ THIS IS A PROMISE
WITH A CATCH ♪♪

26:21.448 --> 26:28.288
♪♪ ONLY IF YOU'RE LOOKING
CAN IT FIND YOU ♪♪

26:30.057 --> 26:37.064
♪♪ 'CAUSE TRUE LOVE
IS SEARCHING, TOO ♪♪

26:38.932 --> 26:41.368
♪♪ BUT HOW CAN IT RECOGNIZE YOU ♪♪

26:41.401 --> 26:47.207
♪♪ UNLESS YOU STEP OUT
INTO THE LIGHT, THE LIGHT? ♪♪

26:47.241 --> 26:52.813
♪♪ DON'T BE SAD,
I KNOW YOU WILL ♪♪

26:52.846 --> 26:55.415
[ DOOR CREAKS ]

26:55.449 --> 26:58.986
♪♪ BUT DON'T GIVE UP UNTIL ♪♪

26:59.019 --> 27:02.189
♪♪ TRUE LOVE WILL FIND YOU ‐‐ ♪♪

27:07.127 --> 27:09.663
Nancy: NO, EVERY TIME,
I'M WALKING DOWN THAT TUNNEL ‐‐

27:09.696 --> 27:13.066
EVERY TIME ‐‐ AND ONCE
I FIND OUT WHAT'S AT THE END,

27:13.100 --> 27:15.769
<i>I'LL FIGURE IT OUT THEN,</i>
<i>BUT AT LEAST I'LL KNOW.</i>

27:15.802 --> 27:17.037
<i>I'LL ‐‐ I'LL KNOW.</i>

27:17.070 --> 27:18.305
[ TAPE REWINDS ]

27:18.338 --> 27:20.474
NO, EVERY TIME,
I'M WALKING DOWN THAT TUNNEL ‐‐

27:20.507 --> 27:23.510
EVERY TIME ‐‐ AND ONCE
I FIND OUT WHAT'S AT THE END,

27:23.544 --> 27:26.647
<i>I'LL FIGURE IT OUT THEN,</i>
<i>BUT AT LEAST I'LL KNOW.</i>

27:26.680 --> 27:29.082
<i>I'LL ‐‐ I'LL KNOW.</i>

27:29.116 --> 27:31.752
WHY WOULD YOU NOT WANT TO KNOW?

27:31.785 --> 27:32.953
[ BEEP ]

27:32.986 --> 27:37.090
